CBRE is pleased to exclusively present 50 -52 McLennan Drive, Kensington, for Sale.

This outstanding city fringe property represents an extremely rare opportunity for owner occupiers to secure a substantial two level commercial building of 700sqm* on the doorstep of the CBD and Port of Melbourne.

This high class corporate office and fully equipped commercial kitchen offers the perfect opportunity for plug and play capability for any food operation wanting to expand and grow their business.

Inspections will not disappoint.

Property features include:
+ Fully equipped commercial kitchen
+ 20sqm* freezer
+ Blas freezer
+ 4 separate cool rooms (variant ambient temperatures)
+ 25 metres* of integrated exhaust
+ Separate staff kitchen area
+ 430amps of power
+ Natural gas
+ 4000 litre grease trap
+ 3 individual switchboards
+ Alarm system and cameras
+ Shower and amenities on both levels
+ Storage mezzanine with pallet crane
+ 2x corporate office including managers office

Please contact the exclusive marketing agents for inspections.

*approx.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to present 43 Stubbs Street, Kensington, available For Sale by Public Auction on Thursday 6th July 2017 at 12.30pm on-site.

This modern 279sqm* office/warehouse comprises a two-level office space and clear span warehouse with full amenities including a shower.  The property sits within the Arden-Macaulay Scheme which has been earmarked for re-zoning.

Situated just off Racecourse Road, the prime location gives you access onto City Link and all major arterials. Positioned just 2km* from Melbourne's CBD, the property is perfect for business that needs to be close to the city without the prices.

Public transportation options include the number 57 tram, just 280 metres* from the property and Macaulay Railway Station just 580 metres*.

Features include:

+ Total building area: 279sqm*
+ Office area: 157sqm*
+ Warehouse area: 113sqm*
+ Three (3) car spaces - one (1) on title plus two (2) for exclusive use
+ Modern open plan two-level office
+ Shower
+ Showroom potential
+ Clear span warehouse
+ 3 phase power
+ Container height roller door
+ Alarm system
+ Great natural light
+ Access to major arterials
+ Main road frontage
+ Nearby public transportation

AUCTION - Thursday 6th July 2017 at 12.30pm On-Site

For more information or to arrange an inspection, please contact Guy Naselli 0413 750 744 or Jake George 0421 221 019.
